{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act12side", "eventName": "多索雷斯假日", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DH-4", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "鐵人三項", "storyInfo": "羅德島的幹員們也出現在了會場觀看比賽。\n第二輪鐵人三項比賽開始，鼠膽龍威隊再一次被其他隊伍包圍。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_20_G04_1/bg_20_G04_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "首先，先來一點音樂！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 10, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ddd_intro", "key": "$ddd_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$livecrowd"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，經過一天的等待，我們即將迎來大獎賽的第二輪比賽——鐵人三項！", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "20_I02_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比賽規則十分簡單，先是跑步，再是騎行，最後是游泳！", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "妨礙他人？沒有問題！只要隊伍中有一個人抵達終點就算出線！", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抄近道是被允許的，但是要當心那埋伏在巷道裡的傢伙！他們可不會輕易讓你通過！", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，抵達終點的人，如果沒有通過騎行和游泳的兩個檢查點的話，成績是不被認可的！", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也就是說，選手們可以在比賽開始後轉身就跳入海中游上游輪，但那只會讓你成為全城的笑柄。", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你是個富豪，近地飛行器也是個可選項！", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，如果不討好觀眾的話，可是有可能被投票出局的！", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外，由於第一輪出線的隊伍是十五支，加上一支透過觀眾投票復活的隊伍，第一輪一共出線十六支隊伍。", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因此，第二輪的出線數量將是八支。", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最先抵達游輪的八支隊伍將獲得出線的權利！", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，讓我們接下來有請十六支參賽隊伍登場！", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_20_G04_1/bg_20_G04_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_206_1#8", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_206_1#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好漂亮的海......", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_190_1#6"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_206_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實。", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#8"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來這座城市果然沒白來。", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#8"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_206_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們就在這裡坐下吧。", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#8"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_206_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不然我還是回去吧，會給這裡的其他人添麻煩的......", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_190_1#4"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_206_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別太在意。這座城市好像不太在乎感染者問題的樣子。", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#8"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_206_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然很明顯，這並不是因為他們開明，而是他們不在乎......", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#7"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_206_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，有蘇蘇洛跟著，不會有問題的，對吧？", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_199_1#1"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。艾雅法拉小姐的病症我心裡有數。", "name": "蘇蘇洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_199_1#1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實你與其擔心給別人添麻煩，更應該擔心的是自己。", "name": "蘇蘇洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_199_1#1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你比其他人都要更加久居室內，這不僅對身體不好，對精神衛生也有影響。", "name": "蘇蘇洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_199_1#1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_199_1#6"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也是這一次我作為醫生贊成將艾雅法拉小姐你帶到這裡來的理由。", "name": "蘇蘇洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_199_1#6"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_199_1#7"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每個人都應該擁有享受陽光的權利。", "name": "蘇蘇洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_199_1#7"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_206_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是。", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#8"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_206_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然博士那邊也是遇到了麻煩，但是隔著螢幕聽說他們在度假那叫什麼事啊。", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們艾雅法拉也該有個休假才對。", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_206_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有，我是自願做地質研究的，而且要是耽誤大家......", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_190_1#2"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_206_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，你就別操心了。", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#8"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_206_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們來這邊也是有正當理由的，羅德島想要在這座城市設立辦事處，一直沒有得到這座城市市長的同意。", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#7"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭讓我們來再當一次說客。", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#7"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_206_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你就安心在這裡享受比賽節目吧。", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#8"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_206_1#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，謝謝。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_190_1#6"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_206_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，紅呢？", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_206_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_199_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她好像不打算出來，一個人不知道哪裡去了。", "name": "蘇蘇洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_199_1#1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_206_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_199_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，這傢伙出任務以來就是這個樣子，我也習慣了。", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#5"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_206_1#1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，快看，來了來了！", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "largebgtween", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ease": "1", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我們歡迎，鼠膽龍威隊！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$livecrowd"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊哈哈。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是分頭行動？", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鐵人三項賽程很長，各做各的很容易失去聯繫。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其他隊伍裡除了單獨分出人來妨礙其他隊伍，基本上都是共同行動的。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩位要是沒有類似的想法我還是建議一起行動。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒意見。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也可以。動手的時候別妨礙我就好。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原話奉還。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "largebgtween", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ease": "1", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_206_1#4"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是沒想到，一開始看電視我還以為看錯了，沒想到陳也來到了這裡。", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#4"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來她也在度假中，等比賽結束後，我們去和她打個招呼吧。", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#4"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#6"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_190_1#6"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_206_1#1"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，你們先看，我去給你們買點吃的，你們就在這裡不要隨意走動啊。", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_199_1#7"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "蘇蘇洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_199_1#7"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "largebgtween", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ease": "1", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以上就是所有十六支隊伍的介紹。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和第一輪一樣，為了讓觀眾們也享受到參與比賽的樂趣，我們為觀眾們也準備了豐富多彩的投注競猜項目。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位觀眾在官方網站上登入自己的資訊後可以為自己賺一筆外快！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "具體操作流程請參照官方發佈的比賽指南。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第二輪比賽中，我們的嘉賓配置將有所變化。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潘喬先生為了準備第三輪比賽已經先一步前往了遊輪上，他將透過視訊連線的方式和觀眾們對話。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，參賽選手們已經都來到了預備線上，請坎黛拉女士來為我們拉響第二輪的禮炮吧！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "玩得高興點，年輕人們。我宣佈——第二輪比賽，正式開始！", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$fireworks"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G03"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chasing_intro", "key": "$chasing_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#2"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來我們又被盯上了，兩位。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#2"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "速戰速決。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Image", "